      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MIDNIGHT MIRAGE (3) broke her maiden last start by 6 lengths at this track over 350m (20.16). Rates on top again. ZAC SURE CAN (2) was strongly fancied and although drifted back wound up hard to score by 0.8 lengths (17.71) at Taree Super Track in Maiden. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. BARCIA CRUISER (1) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 8th at Casino following on from a second place finish (17.16) there the start prior. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Should be about the mark. TUB STAR (8) is new here but should be in the mix.",
